title: Schulman: Jose Bautista’s reaction was flippin’ genius
text:
Photo: Frank Gunn Toronto Blue Jays' Jose Bautista flips his bat after hitting a three-run home run against the Texas Rangers during the seventh inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Division Series, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Toronto. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) Toronto Blue Jays' Jose Bautista flips his bat after hitting a...
Jose Bautista did not so much fling his bat as tomahawk it in Game 5 of Toronto’s Division Series against the Rangers. It was among the most electric expulsions of emotion ever seen on a major-league field.
